      <title>“和平”的雄性倭黑猩猩实际上可能比黑猩猩更具攻击性</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2426678-peaceful-male-bonobos-may-actually-be-more-aggressive-than-chimps/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
